arcade.sim.profiler

Class ParameterProfiler

  • java.lang.Object
    • arcade.sim.profiler.Profiler
      • arcade.sim.profiler.ParameterProfiler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, sim.engine.Steppable

    public class ParameterProfiler
extends Profiler
    Extension of Profiler to output cell parameter values.

    The output JSON includes:

    • seed: random seed of the simulation
    • config: summary of model setup from toJSON method in Series
    • helpers: list of Helper objects
    • components: list of Component objects
    • timepoints: list of timepoints, where each timepoint contains lists of cell locations and parameter values for each cell
    See Also:
